name: Duskfall AI
description:
If you want to donate towards costs and don't want to subscribe:

https://ko-fi.com/DUSKFALLcrew

If you want to monthly support the EARTH & DUSK media projects and not just AI:

https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk

Discord: https://discord.gg/Da7s8d3KJ7

Updates: This doesn't HAVE to produce catboys, just don't use euler, and don't prompt for it. It's not a perfect model, it has it's issue but it's one of our first!!

This is our larger training model, on a smaller (203 512x512 images) data set of our own art with a focus on the fact that our art, and any stable/midjourney outputs we included in this are related to our Dissociative Identity Disorder.

Want to toy with our art WITHOUT wasting space?
https://civitai.com/models/14846/duskfallcrews-art-style-lora

Testing space on huggingface: https://huggingface.co/spaces/Duskfallcrew/duskfallai_webui

If you like what you see on our trained (not merged) models go here: https://www.patreon.com/earthndusk
